  <h2>Worth Asking</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>What system type suits my site, and why?</li>
    <li>What does the project include — and what would be extra?</li>
    <li>What is the expected timeline and sequence?</li>
    <li>How will access and property restoration be handled?</li>
    <li>What approvals apply, and who handles them?</li>
  </ul>

